com.here.android.mpa.common

Interface OnEngineInitListener


  • public interface OnEngineInitListener
    Represents a listener to provide notification of the engine status upon completion of initialization.
    See Also:
    MapEngine.init(Context, OnEngineInitListener)

    • Method Detail

      • onEngineInitializationCompleted

        void onEngineInitializationCompleted(OnEngineInitListener.Error error)
        A callback indicating that map engine initialization has completed.
        Parameters:
        error - If map engine initialized successfully, returns OnEngineInitListener.Error.NONE. Otherwise, one of the other OnEngineInitListener.Error enum values indicating the reason of factory initialization failure.
